data.description: This beautiful 4bedroom/2bath home is located in The Hammocks subdivision right off Hwy 77. This home has a large family room that opens to a cozy screened in back porch. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances with granite counter tops throughout. The master bathroom has a large walk-in shower along with a whirlpool tub with both his & her walk in closets and vanities. This home is the PERFECT home for a family. Located in a cul-de-sac, it features a large fenced-in backyard, and close proximity to both the A+ rated Mosley High School and Bay Haven Charter Academy (K-8).
